OOC: Forgot about them.

BIC: Deemos: ell, I think we should go back to base, now, so whoever is
coming back should come back now.

Deemos walks back towards the Iron Fist. Shokaract, irratated, follows. The
Mini-Mafia, the team who formed the gestalt Mobster, followed behind
Shokaract. Doom Ice finishes screwing Rizopas' head on, but it falls of
again. So she picks it up and drags him behind her to the Iron Fist. Serge,
depressed with his role in the Alliance, stands there, looking on as Deemos
leaves. Diskus flies up to Deemos.

Diskus: Diskus will help Deemos some way.

Deemos: No you won't.

Diskus: Huh?

Deemos: You may be my oldest cohort but I must admit, you helped a little,
but that's when I figured out that you and Artist were obsolete. Artist is
dead now, but I give you a chance to live. Leave, and don't come back. You
don't own anything you'd leave behind anyway, so just go.

Diskus quickly flies away, transforming to beast mode in flight.

Deemos: Chances are, that the team he joins will get screwed up.

Diskus flew away quickly, sad that Deemos didn't want him anymore. He flew
around looking someplace else for companionship...
